Title: What a Wonderful World
Writer: Abbi Jacobson (created by), Ilana Glazer (created by), Abbi Jacobson, Ilana Glazer
Actors: Abbi Jacobson, Ilana Glazer, Fred Armisen, Nicole Drespel
Plot: When Ilana finds out about a secret, pop-up Lil Wayne concert, she and Abbi hustle their way through New York City to try and scrape together enough money for tickets. No matter how creepy it gets, the girls keep their eyes on the prize.
